---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="BridgeAIChat Quickstart">
  <section class="card">
    <div class="eyebrow">Quickstart</div>
    <h1>Run the first beta</h1>
    <p>Use the app release on your control host, then add agent releases to the devices you want to control.</p>
    <pre>1. Download bridge-app release
2. Run ./run-gateway.sh
3. Open http://localhost:8080
4. Download matching bridge-agent release on another device
5. Edit agent.yaml
6. Run ./bridge-agent -config ./agent.yaml</pre>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
